            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1.svg",
            "grid_image_size": "square",
            "heading": "Your Vision, Your Rules",
            "text": "<p>At Griffin & Co, we do things differently. We are not just retailers; we are makers. When you commission a piece with us, you aren't just buying a product—you are collaborating directly with the artisans to create an individual, enduring legacy that tells your story.</p>",
            "button_link": "",
