            "grid_image_size": "square",
            "heading": "Inclusive & Welcoming",
            "text": "<p>Our motto is simple: whoever you are, whoever you love, and whatever your budget, you are welcome at Griffin & Co. Fine jewellery should be accessible to all, and we are here to guide you with complete respect and zero intimidation.</p>",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text": ""
          }
        }
