            "grid_image_size": "square",
            "heading": "In-House Expertise",
            "text": "<p>As a true maker brand, we handle production in-house. Our team consists of GIA-qualified diamond specialists, master goldsmiths, and skilled CAD designers. Your precious items never leave our premises, ensuring security and unparalleled quality control.</p>",
            "button_link": "",
