            "subheading": "It all begins with",
            "heading": "gemstones",
            "text": "<p>We always begin with the fundamental element of every design: the gemstone. Responsibly sourced from our extensive network of reputable suppliers worldwide, our expertise lies in <a href=\"/collections/all\" title=\"Salt & Pepper Diamond Engagement Rings\">salt and pepper diamonds</a>, <a href=\"/collections/all\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Engagement Rings\">lab-grown diamonds</a>, <a href=\"/collections/all\" title=\"Sapphire Engagement Rings\">teal and blue sapphires</a>, as well as an array of vibrant <a href=\"/collections/all\" title=\"Tourmaline Engagement Rings\">tourmalines</a>.</p><p><br/>Each one is assessed and selected by our team to ensure it meets our quality standards and to ensure it's perfect for your forever ring.</p>",
