    "template_product_info_columns_MtzH7c": {
      "type": "template--product--info-columns",
      "blocks": {
        "image_and_text_apcwgN": {
          "type": "image_and_text",
          "settings": {
            "grid_image_size": "square",
            "heading": "Sourcing Gemstones",
            "text": "<p>We source salt and pepper diamonds, sapphires, lab grown diamonds, mined diamonds and tourmalines from suppliers across the globe. Sapphires sourced in Sri Lanka are typically cut in Sri Lanka, however Montana Sapphires and Australian Sapphires can be cut in their country of origin, or in India's expert cutting facilities. </p><p><br/>Diamonds are mined in many countries including Botswana, Canada, Angola and South Africa. Tourmalines are found in Brazil, Kenya, Madagascar, Namibia and more. Both often find their way to Surat in India, the world capital of cutting-edge gemstone cutting technology, to be cut and polished.</p>",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text": ""
          }
        },
        "image_and_text_4whJQy": {
          "type": "image_and_text",
          "settings": {
            "grid_image_size": "square",
            "heading": "Casting & Metals",
            "text": "<p>Most of our rings are cast at a state of the art facility. Using CAD (Computer Aided Design) technology, we're able to create 3D models of your piece so that it can be printed and cast to our exact specification.<br/></p><p>Our suppliers use recycled gold, which is all classed as 'chain of custody', meaning that it's journey from earth to hand is ethical and fair. Platinum recycling is much less common place, although our supplier is working on this, with much of the platinum used in our pieces mined in South Africa.<br/></p><p>We choose these suppliers due to their advanced facilities, and exceptional working conditions for their staff</p>",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text": ""
          }
        },
        "image_and_text_UiwdiR": {
          "type": "image_and_text",
          "settings": {
            "grid_image_size": "square",
            "heading": "Setting, Polishing & Repairs",
            "text": "<p>All of our centre stone setting, resizing and repairs are done by our trusted gemstone setter, Dimitar, and his team in London's Hatton Garden. <br/></p><p>Dimitar trained in Bulgaria before moving to London to expand his skills. Learning from the best jewellers in the heart of London's jewellery quarter, he quickly gained a reputation for his exceptional craftsmanship. <br/></p><p>We're incredibly lucky to work with Dimitar and his team. It allows us to invest in the future of the industry, and ensures each piece passes through the hands of one of the UK's finest craftspeople.</p>",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text": ""
          }
        }
      },
